
Python Info, *******
How to install packages, ***********
Only install packages inside virtual environments, TIP
To istall the package you need pip installed, 
How to setup virtual environments, ********
virtual envrionments are setup using venv, python -m venv "ENV_DIR"
then to activate it you just run the script in its binary directory, source DIR/bin/activate
If you are already in the directory where you want the virtual environment
you merely need to name the directory for the virt env, python -m venv my_env
